Thng 08/2014, VCS thc hin ti c cu v tr thnh cng ty con ca CTCP Tp on Phng Hong Xanh A&A (Phenikaa) vi t l nm gi hin khong 80%. Hot ng chnh ca VCS l sn xut, kinh doanh  p lt nhn to gc thch anh. Vi 2 dy chuyn sn xut  Bretonstone s dng cht kt dnh t nha polyester (Polyester resin) v nha sinh hc.

- Thng 05/2008: Tng vn iu l ln 129.5 t ng.

- Nm 2009: Tng vn iu l ln 150 t ng.

- Thng 12/2010: Tng vn iu l ln 210.66 t ng.

- Thng 07/2011: Tng vn iu l ln 310.66 t ng.

- Thng 01/2012: Tng vn iu l ln 529.99 t ng.

- Ngy 13/08/2014: Tr thnh cng ty con ca CTCP Phng Hong Xanh A&A (Phenikaa).

- Nm 2017: i tn t Cng ty c phn thch anh cao cp VCS sang tn Cng ty C phn VICOSTONE.

- Ngy 07/08/2017: Tng vn iu l ln 800 t ng.

- Ngy 16/04/2018: Tng vn iu l ln 1,600 t ng.
